A=\{(x, y, z)\in\mathbb{R}^3:x^2+y^2\leq 4\}
p=(a, b, c)\in A^c
B_r(p)\subseteq A^c
(x, y, z)\in B_r(p)
x^2+y^2>4
r=\sqrt{a^2+b^2}-2=||(a, b, c)-(0, 0, c)||-2
||(a, b, c)-(x, y, z)||=\sqrt{(x-a)^2+(y-b)^2+(z-c)^2}
(a', b', c') \in B_r(p)
A
\sqrt{{a'}^2+{b'}^2} \leq 2
\sqrt{{a'}^2+{b'}^2} > \sqrt{a^2+b^2}-r=2
\sqrt{{a'}^2+{b'}^2}
c'=c
r>||(a',b',c)-(a,b,c)|| =||(a',b',0)-(a,b,0)|| \geq ||(a,b,0)||-||(a',b',0)||
A \subset \mathbb{R}^3
(a_n) \in A
a_n \to a
a \in A
a_n = (x_n, y_n, z_n) \in A
a_n \to a = (x,y,z)
x_n \to x, y_n \to y
x^2 + y^2 \leq 4
a \in A
 x_n^2 + y_n^2 \leq 4 
 x_n^2 + y_n^2 \to x^2 + y^2 
